pl.coderslab.entity

Class Bet

  • java.lang.Object
    • pl.coderslab.entity.Bet

  • @Entity
public class Bet
extends java.lang.Object
    Entity representing data stored in table bets in the bet24 database. Also used by Hibernate to build database and sql relations. This entity represents a bet placed by client (user). Each bet is related with one event and one bet offer.
